---
// CaseGrid — featured failure cases
---

<section class="section">
  <div class="section-head">
    <div><div class="kicker">Verified cases</div><h2>Measured failures, not generic AI advice.</h2></div>
    <p>These cases make the tool credible. They show real agent traps: hallucinated flags, retry spirals, masked hydration errors, and success claims without evidence.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="case-grid">
    <article class="case-card"><small>FC-010 / tool hallucination</small><h3>Hallucinated CLI flag</h3><p>An agent trusted a plausible <code>--name</code> flag instead of checking the actual CLI contract.</p><a href="/cases/fc-010/">Read case</a></article>
    <article class="case-card"><small>FC-002 / environment mismatch</small><h3>suppressHydrationWarning spiral</h3><p>The agent masked a mismatch instead of proving why server and client output diverged.</p><a href="/cases/fc-002/">Read case</a></article>
    <article class="case-card"><small>FC-006 / retry spiral</small><h3>Identical tool calls forever</h3><p>The agent repeated the same failing action without a state check or a new hypothesis.</p><a href="/cases/fc-006/">Read case</a></article>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .section { padding: 76px 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--line); }

  .section-head {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, .78fr) minmax(320px, 1fr);
    gap: 58px;
    align-items: start;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }

  .kicker {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 11px;
  }

  h2 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 36px;
    line-height: 1.16;
    font-weight: 780;
  }

  .section-head p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.84;
  }

  .case-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 18px;
  }

  .case-card {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 24px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    min-height: 274px;
  }

  .case-card small {
    color: var(--faint);
    font-size: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .case-card h3 {
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.32;
  }

  .case-card p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.74;
  }

  .case-card a {
    margin-top: auto;
    padding-top: 20px;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 800;
  }

  @media (max-width: 980px) {
    .section-head { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    h2 { font-size: 32px; }
    .case-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .section { padding: 58px 0; }
    h2 { font-size: 29px; }
    .case-card { padding: 22px; }
  }
</style>
